post_text:
Brock ISD student enrollment expected to increase by 500 students by 2024.

From the Superintendent:
"The overall theme of their presentation this year is that Brock is growing and will continue to grow into the next decade."
•Brock ISD is projected to maintain our current growth rate over the next 10 years;
•With this current trend, our projected enrollment will be 1,750 students by the year 2020;
•We should eclipse 2,000 students by the 2023-24 school year;
•In 2028-29, over 2,600 students are projected to be enrolled in our district.
To see the full story please visit the Brock ISD at https://www.smore.com/kj6pq-superintendent-blog?ref=email-content#w-4985872852

